	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - Self - 1 Minute - Magical</p><br><p>Using this ability consumes a use of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.HPrjgPXLsDRBbfsD]{Mark for Death}. You cannot use this ability alongside Mark for Death or any other ranger mark.</p><br><p>While you use the Mark of Affliction, once on each of your turns, when you hit a creature with a weapon attack or damage a creature with a ranger spell, you can attempt to poison them with your magic. This ability ends early if you become &amp;reference[incapacitated apply=false].</p><br><p><strong>[[/save con]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><br><p>This ability uses your ranger spellcasting DC.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[poisoned] until this ability ends. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul>",
			"chat": ""
		},
